meaning_str.bing:
n. 循环；自行车；摩托车；整套
v. 骑自行车；骑自行车旅行
网络. 周期；套曲；周波

循环；自行车；摩托车；整套
骑自行车；骑自行车旅行

周期；循环；自行车；摩托车；一组相关的事物；生命周期；工作周期；生理周期；整个系列（如机器的运转）
循环；周期性发生；骑自行车

1.en: A set of edge-triggered (or equivalent) latches which jointly store the state of a binary value through a clock cycle is termed a register.
1.cn: 用一组沿触发（或等价的）锁存器在一个时钟周期内共同地存储一个以二进制数表示的状态，就称为寄存器。

2.en: Dramatic times lay ahead, but all point towards the end of the cycle and your opportunity to leave duality in its present form.
2.cn: 戏剧性的时刻就在前方，所有重点都朝向这次周期的结束，以及你们以它展现的形式脱离二元性世界的机会。

3.en: You'll discuss with your doctor the symptoms you're experiencing, their relation to your menstrual cycle and any other relevant information.
3.cn: 你可以与医生讨论你的症状，以及它们与你月经周期的关系还有其它的相关信息。

0.en: In China, the New Year can start from like, the middle of January than to the end of February. And this lunar cycle repeats itself every 12 years.
0.cn: 中国的春节那天会在是1月中旬到2月底其间的一天。这种农历的循环每12年重复一次。

1.en: We all know that we are better than the cynicism and the pessimism that is regurgitated throughout Washington, and the 24-hour cable news cycle, not my channel by the way.
1.cn: 我们知道，我们要好过华盛顿政府以及24小时循环播放的有线新闻中的犬儒主义与厌世主义，还好不是我的频道。

2.en: Before you go, consider this. Not only do I have a deep cycle marine battery power source which is more than capable of running our entertainment system, I also have all 61 episodes of the BBC series Red Dwarf and Fiddle Faddle.
2.cn: 等等，考虑下这个，我不但有深循环的海军陆战队电池，这能更好地支持我们的娱乐活动。我还有一共61集的BBC科幻剧《红矮星号》，还有《无聊星人》。

3.en: She said that if you want to break the bad boyfriend cycle, you can do like a cleansing ritual.
3.cn: 她说想要停止与恶男交往的恶性循环，可以举行一个清理仪式。

4.en: Some regulate the cell cycle more effectively than others.
4.cn: 它们中的某些在调节细胞周期上比其他要更高效。

6.en: Today is a good day for a cycle ride. A cycle ride, yippee. Peppa and George love cycle ride.
6.cn: 今天是个骑自行车的好日子。骑自行车，太好了！佩奇和乔治喜欢骑自行车。

7.en: Are you thinking Senate next cycle? No, I'm thinking your district, this cycle.
7.cn: 你在考虑下一轮竞选参议员吗？不，我在考虑本轮竞选你的选区。

8.en: Now, if you assume 15 tampons per cycle and a 28-day cycle. Are you fairly regular?
8.cn: 现在假设你每次用15条，28天一周期，你经期正常吗？

9.en: Normally, cell division follows an orderly process called the cell cycle, which is basically the life cycle of a cell.
9.cn: 一般来说，细胞分裂遵循一个叫做“细胞周期”的有序的进程，也就是一个细胞的生命周期。

10.en: I'm already on one painful cycle. I don't want to get on another one.
10.cn: 我已经有一个痛苦的经期[自行车]了，我不想再多要一个。

11.en: Sheldon, I'm not ready to have a baby. Oh, yes, you are! I track your cycle.
11.cn: 谢尔顿，我还没准备好要孩子。你准备好了！我算着你的生理周期呢。

12.en: Aha. This looks like fun. I'll be able to cycle and watch TV at the same time.
12.cn: 啊哈.这看起来很好玩.我可以一边骑自行车一边看电视。

13.en: Aha. This looks like fun. I'll be able to cycle and watch TV at the same time.
13.cn: 啊哈.这看起来很好玩.我可以一边骑自行车一边看电视。

14.en: Step 1: Find the next date of Chinese New Year, which changes with the lunar cycle.
14.cn: 第一步：找到中国新年之后的一天，这是随着阴历周期的变化而变化的。

15.en: Forgive me if I'm not sympathetic to the fluctuations of your sleep cycle, Mr. Lowe.
15.cn: 抱歉，我没法同情你那不稳定的睡眠状况，罗威先生。

16.en: There's nothing left to map. I've run every inch of it myself. Every cycle. Every pattern.
16.cn: 全部都在这里了，我跑遍了迷宫的每个角落，每一层，每面墙。

17.en: Never mind. I clearly woke you up in the middle of a rem cycle. You're in no state of mind to talk.
17.cn: 没事儿，很明显我在你熟睡的时候叫醒了你，你根本就没心情听我说话。

18.en: Well, don't worry. I'll use the gentle cycle. Okay. Basically, you wanna use one machine for all your whites. Okay?
18.cn: 别担心，我会用轻柔绞洗。好的，你得用一台洗你全部的白衣白衣。

19.en: This redundancy is a good thing because you only need one functioning BRCA1 gene in a cell to regulate the cell cycle.
19.cn: 这种“多余”其实是件好事，因为你虽然只需要一个乳腺癌1号基因工作就能控制细胞周期。
